cdata.name: MIO DIO COIN
cdata.desc:
MIO DIO is a blockchain-based cloud gaming project aiming for a safe, transparent and seamless gaming experience. The MIO DIO platform enables the participants to play different games such as 3DBaccarat, Russian Roulette, Blackjack and so on. During the game, the players are also mining MIO DIO tokens.

The MIO DIO native asset is MIO DIO. The MIO DIO is a payment method within the MIO DIO network.
